messages.message: Hi all — I’ve posted an update on our *Release of the Control Plane v0.1* on workplace — please take a look at our post here (https://instabase.workplace.com/groups/591011288909534/permalink/591043382239658/) and join our workplace group, where we’ll continue to post updates and progress. This will affect anyone who develops and maintains services at Instabase, so please take a read through!
